Bryan Orlando APONTE, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
DEPARTMENT OF REVENUE, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-4628 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. December 18, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

The appellee's motion to dismiss is granted. Case 2D18-4628 is dismissed. The challenged order will be reviewed in case 2D18-4516.

CASANUEVA, LUCAS, and ROTHSTEIN-YOUAKIM, JJ., Concur.
